name: broken procedural 005a
description:
broken procedural project

this project of mine was born a few years ago when I was looking for a creative way 
to find digital effects to mix with my fiery characters, they are a series of works 
that are born by combining simple black and white drawings with a moving grid 
that passes over them , through an algorithm then generates different combinations,
 some of these were so beautiful that I wanted to propose them even by themselves, 
but in the future I will combine them with my digital landscapes and my fiery creatures of the metaverse
